'''Mário Bastos''' (wavutse 1986), uzwi cyane ku izina rya stage '''Fradique''', ni Umukinnyi wa firime muri [[Angola]] .  Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime ''zizwi'' cyane Alambamento, ''Independência'' na ''Ar Condicionado'' .  Usibye kuyobora, ni n'umwanditsi, producer, umuyobozi wungirije hamwe n'umwanditsi.<ref>http://africine.org/personne/fradique-mario-bastos/53081</ref><ref name=":0">http://cinafrica.letras.ufrj.br/index.php/filmes/angola/120-mario-bastos-fradique</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1986 i Luanda, muri [[Angola]]<ref name=":0" />. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu mwaka wa 2008, Fradique yize muri New York Film Academy maze ahabwa impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu buhanzi bwiza (kuyobora) muri Academy ya Art University i San Francisco<ref>http://www.clapnoir.org/spip.php?article1259</ref>.  Muri 2009, yakoze film ye ya mbere ngufi, ''Alambamento'' . Iyi filime yatsindiye igihembo cya Filime ngufi nziza mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Luanda kandi yari ihitamo ryemewe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Vancouver ndetse na Tenerife International Film Festival<ref>http://cinafrica.letras.ufrj.br/index.php/filmes/angola/120-mario-bastos-fradique</ref>. 

Mu mwaka wa 2010, Fradique yashinze isosiyete ikora filimi Geração 80 hamwe na Jorge Cohen na Tchiloia Lara<ref>http://africultures.com/films?no=20754</ref>. Muri 2011, yize muri Berlinale Talent Campus kugirango akomeze amasomo. Kuva mu 2010 kugeza 2015, yakoze kuri documentaire ye ya mbere yuzuye, ''Independência'' <ref>http://africine.org/personne/fradique-mario-bastos/53081</ref>.  Iyi filime yibanze ku rugamba rwo kwibohora rwa Angola nyuma iza gutsindira igihembo cy’umuco wa [[Angola]] ku rwego rwa Sinema. Ifatwa nkimwe muma firime meza yibihe byose muri cinema nyafurika<ref>https://www.buala.org/pt/da-fala/etiquetas/geracao-80</ref>.  <sup class="noprint Inline-Template" style="white-space:nowrap;">&#x5D;</sup> Iyi filimi kandi ngo yabonye iki gihembo kuko Best documentaire muri [[Kameruni|Cameron]] International Film Festival no yari guhitamo Official ku Durban International Film Festival, iLuxor Film Festival Afurika Pan African Film Festival.<ref>https://www.berlinale-talents.de/bt/project/profile/194459</ref> 

Yayoboye kandi amashusho yindirimbo zubuhanzi-abahanzi bo muri [[Angola]] nka Nástio Mosquito na Aline Frazão . Muri 2020, yakoze filime ye yambere yimpimbano, ''Ar Condicionado'', ikaba Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Rotterdam.  Nibwo bwatoranijwe kumugaragaro muri [[Uganda]] mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Friborg mu 2020.  Yakiriwe neza mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime.<ref>https://www.sunnewsonline.com/film-critic-wilfred-okiche-in-sa-for-diff-talent-press/</ref> 

